# Detail View Side Section

The record detail view has a side section (right column on large screens) with two built-in tabs:

- **History** — Field-level change tracking. Shows who changed what and when. Implemented by `RecordHistorySection`.
- **Files** — File attachments. Implemented by `AttachmentsSection`.

## Extension Point

`frontend/src/components/generic/GenericObjectDetailViewSideSection.tsx` is the extension point for the side section.

## Extensibility

These sections are designed to be **extensible**. Adding custom content is **recommended**:

- Add new tabs for domain-specific features (e.g., activity feed, notes, related documents)
- Replace or wrap built-in content when needed
- Keep History and Files as the baseline; extend with additional tabs or cards

